item.title: CVE-2024-23613|2024-01-25T23:32:17.046Z -- Symantec -- Deployment Solution
item.description: A buffer overflow vulnerability exists in Symantec Deployment Solution version 7.9 when parsing UpdateComputer tokens. A remote, anonymous attacker can exploit this vulnerability to achieve remote code execution as SYSTEM.
